<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٩٧٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانَ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">وَشُعْبَةَ </a>قَالَا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1277">حَبِيبٌ </a><span class="c2">(ح)</span> قَالَ: وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5889">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ كَثِيرٍ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1277">حَبِيبٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2228">أَبِي الْعَبَّاسِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3823">عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ عَمْرٍو </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«قَالَ رَجُلٌ لِلنَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: أُجَاهِدُ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> لَكَ أَبَوَانِ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> نَعَمْ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> فَفِيهِمَا فَجَاهِدْ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>